        <h2>A trusted advisor at the intersection of strategy and delivery</h2>
        <p>Technology Strategy &amp; Transformation Leader with 20+ years of experience driving enterprise technology strategy and leading large-scale digital, cloud, and AI-enabled transformations across healthcare and financial services. A proven track record of translating emerging technologies — AI/ML, cloud computing, digital transformation — into actionable strategies, executive-level narratives, and investment priorities that accelerate business outcomes.</p>
        <p>Trusted technology advisor to business leaders, with deep expertise operating in global, highly matrixed, and regulated environments. Recognized for influencing portfolio strategy, aligning cross-functional stakeholders, and delivering scalable innovation — with a continued focus on leveraging data, AI, and modern platforms to improve outcomes and drive enterprise value.</p>
