          <div class="tl-node" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="tl-meta">
            <h3 class="tl-role">Director — Software Engineering (FinTech Transformation)</h3>
            <span class="tl-dates">APR 2018 — MAR 2023</span>
          </div>
          <p class="tl-org">FIS / Worldpay — Cincinnati, OH</p>
          <ul class="tl-bullets">
            <li>Led enterprise-scale digital and AI-driven transformation of customer engagement platforms, implementing cloud-based NLP IVR solutions (Nuance, NICE CXone) and AI-powered chatbots to replace legacy DTMF systems.</li>
            <li>Directed modernization of core technology platforms — Salesforce Classic to Lightning, monolithic APIs to microservices, and NLP-enabled self-service channels.</li>
            <li>Led implementation of fraud and dispute management platforms using Pega, integrating FeatureSpace and Signifyd for card and eCommerce fraud prevention.</li>
            <li>Contributed to Banking-as-a-Service (BaaS) strategy, leading engineering teams supporting core banking deposit platforms for community banks.</li>
            <li>Supported post-merger technology integration across Vantiv, Worldpay, and Mercury Payment Systems, contributing to ~$500M in revenue synergies.</li>
            <li>Delivered complex technology portfolios ($1M–$10M+) using SAFe Agile across globally distributed engineering teams.</li>
            <li>Established innovation labs and led POC/POV initiatives across AI/ML, automation, Salesforce, Pega, and microservices.</li>
          </ul>
